==Esperanto==
===Etymology===
Esperanto ''[[i-]]''(indeterminate [[:Category:Esperanto correlatives|correlative]] prefix) + ''[[-u]]'' (correlative suffix of individuals)

===Correlative===
'''iu''' (''plural'' '''[[iuj]]''', ''accusative singular'' '''[[iun]]''', ''accusative plural'' '''[[iujn]]''')

# [[some]], [[someone]] (indeterminate correlative of individuals)
#: Like other indeterminate correlatives, '''iu''' can be combined with ''[[ajn]]'', the adverbial particle of generality. '''''Iu''' ajn'' thus means ''[[any]]'' or ''[[anyone]]''.

